tasks.description:
Create apps/server/src/run/RunWriter.ts. Export writeResultFile = Effect.fn('writeResultFile')(function*(modelId, results, variant, rlmMeta?)): Effect<string, never, FileSystem | Path> where rlmMeta = { depth: number; attempts: number } | undefined. Generates timestamp string in format YYYY y MM m DD d.HH h MM m SS s. Writes to apps/server/res/{timestamp}_{safeModelId}.txt where safeModelId = modelId.replace(/[/: ]/g, '_'). File format follows existing BuildResults.ts parseResultFile pattern: model: {modelId}
right: {right}/{total}
variant: {standard|rlm}
[rlm_depth: N]
[rlm_attempts: N]
--- per task lines: - {id}: {score.toFixed(3)} {pass|fail} time={elapsedMs/1000}s[ bits=N][ ref=N]. Returns written file path. Export also: RES_DIR constant.

